\pard\f0\fs28 Annuals. Stems 1-several, usually simple. Leaves entire. Capitula usually solitary. Involucral bracts in 1 row, more or less equal. Receptacle densely hairy, without scales. Outer ligules yellow, reddish-brown on outer face; the inner brownish-purple. Achenes obpyramidal; pappus absent.
